">[26. 4. 1913]</date></correspAction><correspAction type="received"><persName ref="#pmb2121">Schnitzler, Arthur</persName><placeName ref="#pmb50">Wien</placeName></correspAction><correspContext><tei:ref xmlns:tei="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="belongsToCorrespondence" target="#pmb2147">Altenberg, Peter</tei:ref><ref subtype="previous_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="1913-04-25_01">Engländer an Schnitzler, 25. 4. 1913</ref><ref subtype="next_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="1919-01-10_01">Schnitzler an Engländer, 10. 1. 1919</ref></correspContext></correspDesc></profileDesc><encodingDesc><refsDecl><ab>References to Arthur Schnitzler’s diary online consist of the relevant dates only, 
